00:15:56.100 --> 00:15:57.390
Kimin umurunda?

00:15:58.600 --> 00:16:01.020
Buradaki en gürültücü sensin, Sawaragi.

00:16:01.020 --> 00:16:03.560
Ha? Laf sokmayı bırak,

00:16:04.060 --> 00:16:05.360
